199
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:56,080
- You know, this is bullshit.
- No, Mr. Cafmeyer.

200
00:18:56,080 --> 00:18:59,920
This is Israel.

201
00:19:03,760 --> 00:19:07,600
I apologize for the inconvenience.
Security is extra tight this month.

202
00:19:07,600 --> 00:19:11,440
Muslims are making their pilgrimage
to Jerusalem for Ramadan.

203
00:19:11,440 --> 00:19:15,280
- Passport, please.
- Rudy Cafmeyer!

204
00:19:15,280 --> 00:19:17,200
