and picked up your dad.

244
00:21:49,840 --> 00:21:51,760
- Hey, you!
- Let's go!

245
00:21:51,760 --> 00:21:55,600
- Jump in. I'll drive.
- You don't know the way!

246
00:21:56,560 --> 00:21:58,480
